Package: gnome-shell-extension-customize-ibus
Version: 26
License: GPLv3
Vendor: Hollow Man <hollowman@hollowman.ml>
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Hollow Man <hollowman@hollowman.ml>
Depends: gnome-shell, gnome-tweaks
Section: default
Priority: extra
Homepage: https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/4112/customize-ibus/
Description: Customize IBus for orientation, font, ascii mode auto-switch; theme and background picture follow GNOME Night Light Mode.
  在 GNOME Shell 中更改 IBus 的候选框方向、字体、输入法默认语言，主题、背景图片跟随 GNOME 夜灯模式自动切换。
